<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Reset your password</title>
</head>
<body>
    <p>Hello {{ user.firstname }} {{ user.name }},</p>

    <p>You requested a password reset for your Ranked account.</p>

    <p>
        <a href="{{ reset_url }}">Click here to reset your password</a>
    </p>

    <p>Or copy this link into your browser:<br>
        <code>{{ reset_url }}</code>
    </p>

    <p>This link expires at {{ expires_at|date('Y-m-d H:i') }} UTC.</p>

    <p>If you did not request a password reset, you can safely ignore this email.</p>

    <p>— The Ranked Team</p>
</body>
</html>
